This is an Amarok Script to fetch your lyrics from musiXmatch.com

To install this script you will need to:
1. Add you musiXmatch API key in main.js : APIKEY = "YOUR KEY HERE";
2. Tar the musiXmatchLyrics directory as an Amarok script tar: $ tar -czvf musiXmatchLyrics.amarokscript.tar.gz musiXmatchLyrics/
3. In Amarok in the 'Tools' menu select 'Script Manager' then 'Get More Scripts' to browse and download musiXmatchLyrics.amarokscript.tar.gz from your local file system.

Notice that this script is not yet available in kde-apps.org . It will be uploaded there once fully cleaned up and tested.
